NAME
    ldg_cookie - find a cookie in cookie jar.

SYNOPSIS
    int ldg_cookie( long cookie, long *value);

PARAMETERS
        cookie : cookie identificator (eg 'LDGM'),
         value : cookie value.

DESCRIPTION
    returns TRUE if a cookie 'cookie' is in memory and provide
    the cookie value.


